org.onyxplatform.api.java

Class Windows

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.onyxplatform.api.java.OnyxVector
      • org.onyxplatform.api.java.Windows

  • public class Windows
extends OnyxVector
    Windows objects are a set of Window objects that can be used for a given job. Windows derive from OnyxVector.
